 .../overlay/rockchip-rpi-7inch-lcd.dts        | 45 +++++++++++++++++++
 .../overlay/rockchip-rpi-cam-imx219.dts       | 22 +++++++++
 .../overlay/rockchip-rpi-cam-ov5647.dts       | 30 +++++++++++++
